  "title": "Windows 11 Migration Support (Floorwalker / End User Support)",
  "description": "<p>📢 Hiring: Windows 11 Migration Support (Floorwalker / End User Support)</p><p></p><p>📍 Location: Singapore (Onsite)</p><p>⏳ Duration: 3 Months (Extendable)</p><p>✅ Eligibility: Singapore Citizens / PR only</p><p>⚡ Notice Period: Immediate joiners preferred</p><p></p><p>🔧 Role Highlights:</p><p>• End-user support during Windows 11 migration</p><p>• Pre & post-migration support and testing</p><p>• Troubleshoot Windows 10/11, hardware & applications</p><p>• Incident logging & tracking in ServiceNow (SNOW)</p><p>• Coordinate with desktop/admin & global teams</p><p>• Participate in migration calls & daily reporting</p><p>• Flexible shifts (weekends / early / late hours as needed)</p><p></p><p>💡 Requirements:</p><p>• Strong Windows 10/11 end-user support experience</p><p>• Exposure to OS migration projects preferred</p><p>• Good communication & proactive attitude</p><p></p><p>📩 Send Resume to: muthumala@lionandelephants.com</p>",
